President Trump to attend DeSantis rally at Hertz Arena

A sources confirmed that President Trump will attend a rally for Ron DeSantis at Hertz Arena on Wednesday, Oct. 31.
Wednesday, October 24th 2018, 1:33 PM EDT by A.J. King
Updated:
Wednesday, October 24th 2018, 5:10 PM EDT
via CNN

A source confirmed to NBC2 that President Donald Trump will attenda rally for Ron DeSantis at Hertz Arena on Wednesday, Oct. 31.

Trump has shown public support for DeSantis many times and will make this appearance to try and make sure Republicans secure a midterm victory in Florida.

A recent CNN poll showed Democrats were in the lead with two weeks before the general election.

Thevenue -- formally known as Germain Arena -- is located in Estero at11000 Everblades Parkway.

The rally begins at 7 p.m. You can register for tickets here.
